\begin_inset Formula $\varphi:\ G/H\mapsto G/K$
\end_inset

 формулой 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi(gH)=gH\cdot K=gK
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
Тогда 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi(g_{1}H\cdot g_{2}H)=g_{1}K\cdot g_{2}K=\varphi(g_{1}H)\cdot\varphi(g_{2}H)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
То есть 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
