\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
То есть 
\begin_inset Formula $\ker\varphi=\left(K/H\right)\triangleleft\left(G/H\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Тогда по основной теореме 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Im\ \varphi=G/K\cong\left(G/H\right)/\left(K/H\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

