\begin_inset Formula $\varphi:\ F_{n}\mapsto G_{n}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi(f_{i})=g_{i}$
\end_inset

 и 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi:\ G_{n}\mapsto F_{n}$
\end_inset

